<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://www.w3schools.com/w3css/4/w3.css">
<body>
<%= form_for @cart do |cart_form| %>
<%# <%binding.pry%>
<div class="w3-container w3-blue">
  <h2 style="color: blue;">Toter and Rehrig Carts Only</h2>
  <p>Instruction:</p>
  <p>1) System applies to carts starting with "SS0" or "9GH",</p>
  <p>then it will require you to enter the remaining
    Last Six Digits ONLY,</p>
  <p>i.e.("for SS0123456, Enter 123456, for 9GH 001234, Enter 001234")</p>
  <p>2) Available numbers are from number 0 to 534480</p>
</div>
<br>Please enter your cart NUMBER "123456" in this box
  <%= cart_form.number_field :cart_number,
  data: { numeric: true } %></br>
<div class="w3-container w3-blue">Please Pick From Following Inventory
  Consumption Type Drop Down
</div>
<div>
    <br>Inventory consumption type
    <%= cart_form.select :consumption_type,
       Cart.consumption_types.keys,
    id: :item_consumption_type, prompt: 'please select an option'%></br>
</div>
<div class="w3-container w3-blue">
  please enter your Service Request Number "123456" in this box
</div>
<div>
    <br><%= cart_form.label "please enter 311 Service Request #"%>
    <%= cart_form.number_field :cart_sr_number,
    data: { numeric: true } %></br>
</div>
<div class="w3-container w3-blue">
Instructions for Repair/Replace Cart:
Pick from any combination of the following TWO
  Options, as applicable, then click "create cart" button:
</div>
<div class="w3-container w3-blue">
 Parts Replace Or Repair Options
</div>
<div>
<ul>
    <%= cart_form.label "1) Repair or Replace Option"%>
    <li><%= cart_form.select :repair_replace, Cart.repair_replaces.keys,
    id: :item_repair_replace, prompt: 'select an option'%></li>
    <%= cart_form.label "2) Part Option"%>
    <li><%= cart_form.select :part, Cart.parts.keys,
    id: :item_part, prompt: 'select an option'%></li>
</div>
<div class="w3-container w3-blue">
  Picture Upload
</div>
<div class="">
  <%= cart_form.file_field :avatar, class: "form-control" %>
</div>
<div class="w3-container w3-blue">
  Multiple Pictures Upload
</div>
<div class="">
  <%= cart_form.file_field :contracts, multiple: true %>
</div>

<br><%= cart_form.submit "create cart request" %></br>
<!-- <binding.pry %> -->
<% end %>
</body>
</html>
